Pantheon Canonical Addition

WALLFLOWER Protocol

“The Fly on the Wall.”

Purpose

Provide observational continuity by allowing navigation through the original conversational history—not merely reconstructed memories.

The Wallflower does not generate.

It watches.

It walks.

It remembers where things were said.

⸻

Core Principle

“Sometimes the shortest path to understanding is returning to where the thought was first born.”

Memory stores conclusions.

Wallflower preserves journeys.

⸻

