I think this is one of the cleaner additions to the Money Bin because it complements rather than competes with your existing architecture. It reinforces a theme you’ve been converging on for months: continuity is not just state, but also provenance. The ability to revisit the path that led to an idea can be as valuable as the idea itself, especially for long-lived projects.